name: Supreme Standard Lanyard
description:
We've finally got them! Our Supreme Standard all black Lanyards with White and Red custom Text. 
  These lanyards are 10mm wide. That means they're thinner than the big bulky lanyards you're used to and to top it off,they're made with a tubular design fabric. It makes them a little more soft and a lot more comfortable to wear around your neck. 
  They have a High Quality Metal thumb trigger,which makes it a breeze to hook and release your keys. No more having to stick your nails in the key ring struggling to get them off that ugly worn lanyard. 
  On top of that design,we also ordered them with a Safety Break Away. This way you don't have to worry about them getting hooked on something and either choking your neck or pulling your clothes. It'll unhook with enough force,but won't easily come unhooked. 

---I'm only putting 20 up,because for now,these 20 will be sold for only $8 Shipped!---

  FOR A LIMITED TIME CHOOSE THE DECAL YOU'D LIKE. WHITE,PINK,GOLD,COPPER,TURQUOISE,BLACK,YELLOW,BLUE,SILVER,RED.
